<li><a href="http://www2.sims.berkeley.edu/research/projects/how-much-info-2003/index.htm" class="external text" title="http://www2.sims.berkeley.edu/research/projects/how-much-info-2003/index.htm" rel="nofollow">How Much Information? 2003</a> an attempt to estimate how much new information is created each year (study was produced by faculty and students at the <a href="/wiki/UC_Berkeley_School_of_Information" title="UC Berkeley School of Information" class="mw-redirect">School of Information Management and Systems</a> at the <a href="/wiki/University_of_California_at_Berkeley" title="University of California at Berkeley" class="mw-redirect">University of California at Berkeley</a>.)</li>
